===Noun===
'''[[risk]] [[management]]'''
# A management technique that combines [[risk assessment]] with the development of [[strategies]] to [[minimize]] or [[manage]] that risk.
# Risk Management is the process of measuring, or assessing risk and then developing strategies to manage the risk.

====Origin====
This term relates very specifically to the field of study denoted by the term and as such is a usage specific term.

